description:
*Available in: English, French, German, & Spanish*

Sitting down somewhere? Tired? Stressed? Or just want something for your kids to look at? Well now you can have an amazing aquarium in the palm of your hands! Just open the app, tap the button when you're ready, and a beautiful high quality aquarium fills your screen!
